{"tid":233689,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［Wow 左未］綾瀨線宣佈小說化！","createTime":"2017-05-07T16:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T03:22:03.000Z","uid":4997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e21cc87e0c3862b36a567f4cb730c4cf587f6efc","tid":233689,"uid":4997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"5月5日於日本德島縣舉辦的「マチ★アソビ」活動上，《我的妹妹哪有這麼可愛》公開了要將 PSP遊戲《我的妹妹哪有這麼可愛 Portable》中的綾瀨路線添筆小說化，以及推出綾瀨版的對話AI育成計畫《我的老婆（綾瀨）哪有這麼可愛（俺の嫁（あやせ）がこんなに可愛いわけがない）》的消息，光是看到這樣的內容，就能預想喜歡「新垣綾瀨」的人們一定非常振奮。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲改編文庫小說版第一波「綾瀨if」，將會以《俺妹》PSP遊戲的劇情為基礎去添筆修正，官方同時也告知了如果小說反應不錯的話，就會將企劃陸續推出第二波。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2502/2502407.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2502%2F2502407.jpg&h=6c13ae2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《我的老婆（綾瀨）哪有這麼可愛》則是這次公開的特別企劃，官方將會公開一項關於綾瀨的育成問答遊戲，讓每個使用者試著想像「如果是綾瀨的話」會怎麼回答，官方會再透過這些問答內容去優化對話AI，屆時由參與活動的人共同創作的「My Lovely天使綾瀨炭」就會出現在大家的眼前。<br />\n<br />\nSource:  <blockquote><a href=\"http://game.ettoday.net/article/918207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F918207.htm&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=6a71eccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://game.ettoday.net/article/918207.htm</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2471f496a06dd085210a9a90ab4073907cc7b27c","tid":233689,"uid":63834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:14:08.000Z","msg":"黑貓黨表示：..."},{"pid":"9b199b73864da99e2ee1ecee6bd81709d12109f6","tid":233689,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T19:14:49.000Z","msg":"wow左"},{"pid":"00c21bd938c66e78798627f77982ea4882f7abd6","tid":233689,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"[wow] <br />\n你開post問不如search下"},{"pid":"2a0126a59a398e052710d67e85de5d5f2c7c1193","tid":233689,"uid":32128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply